{"tid":2013812,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"百貨公司停開兩月　皮貨發霉損失慘重","createTime":"2020-05-12T14:15:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-12T14:30:45.000Z","uid":28114,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"b9ed321a6bc28280e6694114e21fd378e4d03519","tid":2013812,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T14:15:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/aeanews/20200512/photo/bkn-20200512220052436-0512_00912_001_01p.jpg?20200512220338\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Faeanews%2F20200512%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20200512220052436-0512_00912_001_01p.jpg%3F20200512220338&h=38d1c1fd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n皮鞋及皮袋都嚴重發霉。<br />\n<br />\n馬來西亞封城近兩個月，商城終可重開，惟有民眾發現百貨公司內的皮製貨品慘遭劫難，不論平貴統統長滿霉菌，周日（10日）將照片上傳至社交網後引起熱議。網民猜測商城因沒開冷氣而濕度大增。有自稱行內人士則指，皮貨長期不用而發霉是正常情況，亦證明百分之百是真皮所製。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/aeanews/20200512/photo/bkn-20200512220052436-0512_00912_001_02b.jpg?20200512220338\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Faeanews%2F20200512%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20200512220052436-0512_00912_001_02b.jpg%3F20200512220338&h=8c2b3d70&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n照片可見貨架皮貨幾近全軍覆沒。照片可見貨架皮貨幾近全軍覆沒。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/aeanews/20200512/bkn-20200512220052436-0512_00912_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Faeanews%2F20200512%2Fbkn-20200512220052436-0512_00912_001.html&d=EvsgW2mpOVZdTd1tTx%2BWmK7%2FPCTF2%2B9SGuy7I2Db2XM%3D&h=cefecc9d\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/aeanews/20200512/bkn-20200512220052436-0512_00912_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"e60481cd789a3dc5b2ba9c48f76862b53a7b0f93","tid":2013812,"uid":63154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T14:17:50.000Z","msg":"真皮確認<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c0203601a6dc5cd4060f393210eaa7ce6b98c4a","tid":2013812,"uid":16676,"lik